name: Dynamorio
body:
Global setup:
set up git
git config --global user.name "huyanshuhan"
git config --global user.email huyanshuhan@gmail.com

next steps:
mkdir dynamorio
cs dynamorio
git init
touch readme
git add readme
git commit -m 'first commit'
git remote add origin git@github.com:huyanshuhan/dynamorio.git
git push -u origin master
